{"tid":772640,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我無得去遊學團","createTime":"2018-08-09T02:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T09:50:02.000Z","uid":181819,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa68973f04b473dc5f61bf33365712783190d66d","tid":772640,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"我16歲 過埋暑假就升中四<br />\n學校搞左個遊學團暑假去澳洲14日<br />\n團費9000$ 學校資助左一半<br />\n滿心歡喜同老母講想參加<br />\n佢一句撻埋黎話唔得<br />\n我問點解<br />\n佢話屋企冇錢 得老豆一個做野<br />\n要交租 電費水費好貴 個個月都冇淨<br />\n叫我生性 暑假去小童群益會到學下野就算啦 <br />\n幾百蚊都仲負擔到<br />\n我唔服氣<br />\n點解張文傑(我同學)屋企人又比錢佢去呀 佢又係住呢條村 <br />\n我老母即刻冇聲出 <br />\n我嬲到離街出走左<br />\n依家係樓下公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我未出過國 飛機都未搭過 真係好想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71febd3a6c0b854557f652206d03e16404b901be","tid":772640,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:35:53.000Z","msg":"即刻屌鳩佢<br />\n窮人學咩人生仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926c9eb15b4526fd6bf6e5ab6c0e652bf45bf233","tid":772640,"uid":33620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:37:55.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"7d11cbb81ec4e2bb07a7a94cccfc21608c37bd1f","tid":772640,"uid":6352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係假膠，就規勸你一句：各有前因莫羨人。手"},{"pid":"5435900658f8781020c131b2b10151fa71daffb9","tid":772640,"uid":88888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"因為你老母知你係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bf636a69b5f65a3aaa079bfbb5ed1107dae677","tid":772640,"uid":88888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5435900658f8781020c131b2b10151fa71daffb9","tid":772640,"uid":88888,"like":3,"di